<div><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">From: Tjomme T Henny [</span><a href="mailto:tjomme@prisma-it.com" style="font-family: Calibri;">mailto:tjomme@prisma-it.com</a><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">] </span></div>
<div><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">Sent: woensdag 3 december 2014 08:49</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">To: Jorrit Wulffers</span></div>
<div><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">Subject: [TT 28919] - Acknowledgement - Re: Uitnodiging voor deelname aan een onderzoek -- [EMAIL IMPORT]</span></div>
<div><br style="font-family: Calibri;" /></div>
<div><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">Jorrit,</span></div>
<div><br style="font-family: Calibri;" /></div>
<div><span style="font-family: Calibri; float: none;">wellicht vind jij dit interessant?</span></div>
<div><br style="font-family: Calibri;" /></div>
